Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:20.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Last week, the chief secretary was issued illegal donations
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.63,0:00:25.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This week, it'll be the rant on that minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:28.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why it's only me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:31.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the one that have to face those reporters that\Nwant to tear me apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:34.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.14,0:00:38.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There are particularly two nasty reporters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:43.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Those guys when I have a troubled face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:46.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,they grin..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.66,0:00:50.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's bullying!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.16,0:00:52.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,More..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:55.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Those guys, are space aliens!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:59.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because space aliens don't understand\Nthe human feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:03.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,They hurt me cold blooded
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:09.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. I wish there was a sort of a barrier\Nto protect me from those guys
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.66,0:01:12.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's make it.\N{\3c&H585657&}eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:15.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To repel any nasty alien attack
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:17.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,let's create a barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:19.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The button is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:23.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,May I? If you press this button,\Nyou'll become the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:25.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There will be no fear to any alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:27.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.66,0:01:29.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:31.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.13,0:01:34.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, for this sudden request,\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:36.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's good, just wait outside a bit more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:38.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., there is still a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:40.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,of things I want you to hear,\Nif you could prolong this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:43.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How about having lunch? I'll treat you\N{\3c&H585657&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:46.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But I already have plans.\N{\3c&H585657&}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:49.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ike-san, the button for the barrier.\NPlease don't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:50.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:53.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, if you excuse me.\N{\3c&H585657&}Ah Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:55.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.14,0:02:10.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:13.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Why don't you come at least once to my examining room?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:15.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"examining room?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:18.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"At lunch break, we'll have a cup of tea together."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:28.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, what would you like to do for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:30.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,After all,\Nyou want the daily meal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:32.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Again?\N{\3c&H585657&}Yeah, because in the daily meal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:35.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you have something for each day.\N{\3c&H585657&}I brought it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:38.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's unusual.\N{\3c&H585657&}Ah, that means you're economizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:41.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because you're cheated by the geisha\Nwith 3 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:42.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's that story?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The money has been properly returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:48.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're happy for what?\N{\3c&H585657&}But..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:51.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That might be the trick, right?\N{\3c&H585657&}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:53.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Once she returns the money, you trust her
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:57.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,next time, she'll demand a lot of money.\NWell, that's the common trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:03:00.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so?\NThank you very much for the advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:02.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry\Nthe daily will be sold out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:04.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\3c&H585657&}Ah, I'll hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:06.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, what were you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:14.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ask Yumeno to come.\N{\3c&H585657&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:16.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, those bad manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here, it's done.\N{\3c&H585657&}do this properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:21.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:25.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Lunch's ready
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:27.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll go just now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:30.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The soba will grow stale.\NPlease come soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:34.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:04:08.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She's not coming today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:20.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Rintaro, are you coming\Nto the afternoon conference, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:22.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:32.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:40.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:44.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Yumeno-san"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:50.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:05:00.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:06.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Yumeno-san"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:12.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:14.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The 7 million yen, 7 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I KNOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:24.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She hung up..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:26.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Reach!\N{\3c&H585657&}Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Almost reach.\N{\3c&H585657&}Enough..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:32.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah bring your brains!\NIt's always the same with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's too persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:43.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That Dr. Hino
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:45.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that psychiatry Dr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:51.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Report to the police..\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:55.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I thought about asking the decision\Nfrom the professors of psychiatry first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:58.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About Kobayashi Yumiko-san,\N35 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:01.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She fell from the stairs and hit his left side of the abdomen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:04.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the results of the MRI revealed\Na traumatic spleen injury
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:08.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,By means of an emergency laparotomy, we've removed the spleen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:13.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,However, it's unlikely that because of the fall,\Nshe would have multiple bruises..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:16.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She also came half a month ago for chest bruises.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:19.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The cause was the same as this time,\Nfalling from the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:21.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So?\N{\3c&H585657&}DV.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:24.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There is a possibility that she is suffering\NDomestic Violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:27.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why the police.\N{\3c&H585657&}Let's quit this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:30.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The Dir. dislikes this kind of cases the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?\N{\3c&H585657&}I didn't say a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:36.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Certainly, it's because it was troublesome last year,\Nit was a false accusation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,False accusation?\N{\3c&H585657&}The nurses
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:41.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,without authorization from above,\Nreported the suspicion of DV.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It was just an act performed by the wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:46.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She just wanted to break up with him, and made the bruises by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:51.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, the director has been struggling\Nwith the husband's nearly lawsuit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:55.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, this time is clear by the marks\Nthat she has been beaten by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:57.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've seen these type of injuries for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:07:00.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If we do not protect the victim early from the DV problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:04.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There is also a possibility that the risk extends to life.\N{\3c&H585657&}I know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:06.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Quit the report.\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:10.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because it's troublesome?\N{\3c&H585657&}Excuse me! She is also my patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:14.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even in adults, because they are afraid of the DV perpetrator\Nthey don't want to recognize..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Residents stay in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,well..\NYes??
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:28.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,May I ask to talk with Kobayashi Yumiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:32.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's a face that will likely judge without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:36.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Be sure to ask permission from Prof. Hasumi\Nif you by any chance want to report the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:38.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:42.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,These are very beautiful flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:46.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,They are called "preserved flowers".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:48.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My husband brought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:51.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Really?\NThat's a nice husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:53.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:57.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This one, what flower is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:08:00.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Gerbera. (African daisy)\N{\3c&H585657&}It's a gerbera!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:02.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,haha\N{\3c&H585657&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:06.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's just that the Dr.\Ndoesn't know a gerbera..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:09.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:12.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, you're Dr...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:15.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry about the late introduction,\NI'm a psychiatrist, my name is Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:17.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,psychiatrist ..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I heard that you fell down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is it that you would like to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,May I ask you one question?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:28.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is something we ask everyone\Nwith the similar injuries you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:32.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did someone exert some sort of violence over you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:33.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:36.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did you suspect it was DV?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:39.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My husband is a member of the Tokyo Metropolitan Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:44.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He holds his work proudly and diligently,\Nwith a strong sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:47.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He is also very respected by many\Nof his subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:50.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's not the type of person that would use violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:56.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see,\Nit's nice that you could clarify it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:09:00.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If there's anything that is troubling you,\Nplease feel free to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:03.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want to give Yumiko-san \Nthe strength
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:06.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,so you can recover immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:08.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being so gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:10.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:24.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My wife is under your care,\NI'm Kobayashi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:26.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm a psychiatrist, my name is Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:29.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I came to talk a little about the symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:32.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:35.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.\N{\3c&H585657&}Thank you, we'll be under your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:43.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I brought you a change of clothes｡\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:46.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, why didn't you ask her\Nmore deeply about the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:49.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My favorite comedian has this saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:53.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"To hear too much is useless when the person is not talking"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:55.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But\Ndon't you think she's lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but Kawakami-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:00.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The person in question has denied the DV.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:03.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did you drop the ballpoint pen on purpose, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:05.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\3c&H585657&}Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:08.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,DV victims would overreact to even minor sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:11.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But Yumiko-san did not react.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:14.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, police officers usually suffer\Nfrom stress and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:17.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,there is a theory that they often become DV perpetrators.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:19.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If it's DV and we don't grasp evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,before she leaves the hospital,\Nit may be serious..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:24.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,First, let's get close to the patient's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:27.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to judge based on preconceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:35.69,Self tought,,0,0,0,,So, now let's move forward with no fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:39.65,Self tought,,0,0,0,,I'm your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:43.17,Self tought,,0,0,0,,This is a story of a doctor that saves
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:45.65,Self tought,,0,0,0,,the lost sheep of this modern era.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:55.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:59.67,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the late introduction,\NI'm a psychiatrist, Hino Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:10.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:31.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:34.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How about 500,000 yen?\N{\3c&H585657&}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:36.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't it Crocodile?\NMoreover, with no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:39.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,500 000 is too cheap, isn't it?\N{\3c&H585657&}But you see, in the market..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:42.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, I'm in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:45.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:48.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,¥ 505,000.\N{\3c&H585657&}Please, 510 000!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:56.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Haven't you eat yet?\N{\3c&H585657&}Ah yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's okay to bring your lunch to the examination room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,People who are traumatized
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:06.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,there are many times when they aren't able\Nto come on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:08.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want to wait for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:11.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., there's no meaning in that\Nif your health is damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:15.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\3c&H585657&}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:17.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kaoru-san\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:19.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you like gerberas?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:22.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I like them, they are cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:25.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Gerbera has a lot of meaning\Nin the language of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:27.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Language of flowers? eh..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:29.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, Dr.\Nplease eat properly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:32.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, see you tomorrow\N{\3c&H585657&}See you tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:35.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the language of flowers..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:43.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:47.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumechiyo-san.\N{\3c&H585657&}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:53.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is there anything wrong?\NIt's a rare match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:55.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If there's something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:59.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What did you intend by calling Yumeno to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's about that..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:04.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The fact is that..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:07.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wanted to have an opportunity to talk to Yumeno-san,\Nit was an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:10.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to have a talk? Yumechiyo, that's an outing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:14.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that will be outing,\Nnot a medical examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:16.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The charging will be ten times the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:19.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Plea..Please wait a minute! \N{\3c&H585657&}It's a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:22.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's just that Yumeno it's an important geisha at our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:24.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Either if you meet at the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:28.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,or if you go outside, \Nplease you should not extend your words so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:30.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:35.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno found your invitation\Na little too frequent, let's say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:38.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In short you're too nagging.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:41.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You should go moderate on this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:44.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,From Yumeno's point of view,\Nyou're just a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:48.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About the DV matter..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The husband seems to be a member\Nof the Metropolitan Police Department, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:53.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,draw back from this\Nand leave it to the surgery department.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:55.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:14:00.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disturb you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,En-sama, my stomach is making noise already..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:08.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You,\Nhaving the Dir. and the Okiya's mother..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:10.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Those two are a little tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:13.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,They ARE, and more I\Nwas treated as if I was a person obsessed with sex,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's ultra upsetting!\Nto say that for real
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you're not obsessed with it, are you?\NI'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:20.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's a strange women.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:23.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,inviting you so excitedly,\Nthen abruptly refusing you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:26.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The service is becoming exceedingly crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:33.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Stop getting involved
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:35.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:37.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, what is it that you have been eating,\Nthat..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:40.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's a Pork shogayaki sandwich\N{\3c&H585657&}eh, did you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:42.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, although\Nit's just inserting it between bread, but
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:44.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:49.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,nah, as expected this is better.\N{\3c&H585657&}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:53.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I heard it,\Nthat you have been recommended to become a professor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:57.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who told you that?\N{\3c&H585657&}I have many connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:15:01.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you're able to properly ascend the stairs\Nthat are in front of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:04.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you're going to be able to save as many patients as possible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:08.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you penetrate such policy\Nit's convenient, it'll give you influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:12.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Listen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:15.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do not get involved with that strange woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Today too, you've stayed in the hos..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:27.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Today too, you've stayed in the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:29.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:33.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kawakami-san just, just a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:38.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,eh..what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:41.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's bad Kawakami-san\Nto be watching at the patients?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:43.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, who will defend them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're going to far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:47.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:52.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's the first time I'm not able\Nto save the patient I'm in charge of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:56.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The DV victims\Nneed the help of a third party!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good morning.\N{\3c&H585657&}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:03.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, regarding the matter of\Nthe consultation with head detective Shimada
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:06.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll immediately extend to you the report.\NYes, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:08.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:20.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:23.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good morning.\N{\3c&H585657&}Ah good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This time I'll introduce myself properly,\NI'll be under your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:28.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I will received it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:32.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, you are a psychiatric doctor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:38.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did you hear it from my wife?\NThe reason that she fell from the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:39.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:41.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:44.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just to have been half asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:46.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:48.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:50.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:53.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're concerned right? about no knowing the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:56.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:17:01.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's just that it seems to me like your wife\Nis hiding something
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:08.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:10.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:12.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just a minute.\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I've kept you waiting.\N{\3c&H585657&}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:39.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You think she is hiding something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:44.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:46.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just, I'm sorry.\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:50.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:55.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh ... I didn't say such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:59.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking!!\NWhose instructions are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:02.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay, just follow my instructions!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:05.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's not possible for him to suppress the anger,\Nalso has very intense emotional ups and downs
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:07.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As it's commonly seen in DV perpetrators.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:13.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry\N{\3c&H585657&}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's has been a little busy at work lately.\N{\3c&H585657&}I see
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:21.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're very busy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:26.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, shouldn't you be relaxing at home for a couple of hours..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:27.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, I really can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:30.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we don't have any children,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:33.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,at this moment, my wife situation\Nwill just give me lonely thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:35.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:38.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here, take it\NOh, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:40.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:45.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, I think that your wife has become \Nsomeone you want to cherish
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:47.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,with great care, right? Kobayashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:51.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I recall have seen the preserved flowers \Nin her hospital bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:54.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh No, no, that's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:59.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In this room..\Nwill you be able to properly rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:05.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well, even though it's a bit of poor sleep,\Nit's still a little better than having to return home..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:10.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And what about your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:14.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Has she been lately in a stressful situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:16.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, I couldn't say..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:20.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If one of us is full of stress,\Nis more likely to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:24.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That would be all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:27.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since I have to stay.\N{\3c&H585657&}Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:30.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:38.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Mizushima
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:41.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your wound looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:44.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why did you send me that psychiatric Dr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:45.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:51.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's because you suspected of DV from my husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:20:00.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That is a complete insult to my husband
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:05.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you going with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:09.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About that..\N{\3c&H585657&}On no account,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:14.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,we are being affected by that at all.\NPlease tell Dr. Hino that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:18.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yuriko, I'm leaving now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:22.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah..have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:33.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, hello En-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:36.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Again, I have another consultation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:39.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to hear anything from the cute Yumeno
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:42.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's just that tomorrow I have a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:45.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh..again an adult reunion\NI can't go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:47.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:49.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll go for sure next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:51.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You promise?\N{\3c&H585657&}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:53.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:59.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno, we have inquired\NDr. Hino very sharply, we've told him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:02.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you continue being so insistent,\Ndon't come to the geisha house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:04.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:12.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\u1\i0\b1}we want to know about the 7 million quickly{\u0\i1\b0}\N[T/N: written many times]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:23.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Irresponsible Akira-chan,\Nanswer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:26.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's enough, you're drinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:29.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even I..you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:34.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm irresponsible at wanting to wash my feet..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,such a thing..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:44.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We don't get to do only what we\Nlike to do..you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:53.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:55.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thanks..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:59.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Jun-chan, you're a kind guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:05.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hurry, bring me some sake, hurry\N{\3c&H585657&}It's enough..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:09.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Pay those 7 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:11.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?\N{\3c&H585657&}Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:17.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.16,0:22:19.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please take care in your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:20.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We've done for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.62,0:22:22.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. your phone is ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:24.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.63,0:22:28.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here you have.\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.26,0:22:39.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You two, it's okay if I'll leave\Nahead of you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.22,0:22:42.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\3c&H585657&}See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.56,0:22:43.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.18,0:22:47.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:50.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're forgetting your jacket.\N{\3c&H585657&}Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.12,0:22:53.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Until tomorrow then.\N{\3c&H585657&}Until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:22:58.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yasuke
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:01.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:05.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, welcome home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:07.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:14.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:18.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When I told mom that you\Nhad invited me to tea,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:21.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,for some reason it become a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.03,0:23:23.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.71,0:23:26.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's have a pleasant talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:28.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.74,0:23:33.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.48,0:23:36.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:42.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to invite me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.16,0:23:43.79,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.12,0:23:50.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait, if you get in,\Nthen it becomes an outing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.08,0:23:53.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, wait wait, at this point,\Nis it already outing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.40,0:23:56.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay if it's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.32,0:23:59.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see, then come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:02.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm going to put some tea.\NPlease have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.62,0:24:07.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,eh.. then this is Hino-rin's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.63,0:24:11.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of books
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:15.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, what is that you wanted to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.32,0:24:21.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, without asking anything\Nlend me 7 million yen, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.92,0:24:23.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,7 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.28,0:24:25.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't have anyone else to depend on,\Nplease!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.56,0:24:27.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait, but,\NWhy so much money?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.64,0:24:29.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's absolutely necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.40,0:24:33.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Of course, I don't intend to get it for free,\NI..came with the intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.40,0:24:34.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's that intention?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.28,0:24:37.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I won't go home tonight.\N{\3c&H585657&}You won't return home!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.12,0:24:42.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll\Nbecome yours, take me Hino-rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.44,0:24:44.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute,\Nwait a minute, Yumeno-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.84,0:24:45.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.60,0:24:50.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fall in love with me..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.60,0:24:54.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san, please let's calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.48,0:24:56.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understood the part about the money,\Nif there's anything I can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.92,0:24:58.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything that it's at my reach.\N{\3c&H585657&}Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.68,0:24:59.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mizushima!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.16,0:25:02.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.68,0:25:04.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.68,0:25:07.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even so, I'm stopping it,\Nbecause it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.88,0:25:10.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're trying to get money\Nfrom Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.40,0:25:12.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is your purpose?\N{\3c&H585657&}Mizushima, you see..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.12,0:25:13.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Explain it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.40,0:25:16.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,\Nmay I borrow your washroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.92,0:25:18.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Where is it?\N{\3c&H585657&}The washroom, it's..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.92,0:25:19.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Over there..\N{\3c&H585657&}Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.14,0:25:26.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.14,0:25:31.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.56,0:25:36.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Rintaro, you too,\Nthat's the lowest thing for a man to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.48,0:25:38.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.\N{\3c&H585657&}In what I'm wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.00,0:25:41.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is going on? with that girl,\Nshe's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.56,0:25:45.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why..\Nthat's why I wanted to hear her story.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.88,0:25:48.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because I want to know her true face.\N{\3c&H585657&}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.88,0:25:53.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She's hiding her true face in a shadow of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.00,0:25:55.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She said it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.28,0:26:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Always by myself,\Nalways so lonely."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.20,0:26:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always by myself..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.64,0:26:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always so lonely..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.84,0:26:40.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.62,0:26:43.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.68,0:26:45.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.88,0:27:14.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When the SOS sign is out,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.88,0:27:17.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It can not be something that you pretend not to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.65,0:27:34.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.08,0:27:37.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.16,0:27:44.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have a nice day
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.65,0:27:54.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.64,0:27:58.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I do not want to regret anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.68,0:28:02.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You told her, if there was something you\Ncould do to help her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.48,0:28:05.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You probably want to help Yumeno-san with your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.32,0:28:07.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the Dr. Rintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.68,0:28:15.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About that, I was clearly told by\NKobayashi Yumiko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.16,0:28:18.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,On no account,\Nshe wants to have something with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.28,0:28:24.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think there's something awkward with that couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.13,0:28:50.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.24,0:28:52.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.72,0:29:01.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-kun,\Ndo you know the reason why I called you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.88,0:29:02.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.52,0:29:06.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You has been selling that you hear people's stories
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.28,0:29:10.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, the truth is that you don't listen them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.12,0:29:11.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.08,0:29:13.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The patients suspected of DV violence
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.00,0:29:16.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,came to say that they're changing to the police hospital\N as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.04,0:29:19.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumiko-san?\NOur hospital is that much hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.84,0:29:24.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even though they are surgical patients,\Npsychiatrists have been persistently hearing and watching them,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.48,0:29:27.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,for being suspected as a case of domestic violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.40,0:29:31.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't it true that you have been persistently monitoring\Nhusband and wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.52,0:29:33.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No,\Nto say that I persistently listen to them..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.28,0:29:36.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That is something that the other party decides,\Nthat's why I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.16,0:29:40.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's in the pointless talk with the patient,\Nthat the unnecessary problems begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.92,0:29:42.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's not something pointless,\Nit's a necessary talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.84,0:29:45.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Anyway,\NWe are within a few days from the scratch of the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.60,0:29:48.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In the meantime,\Ndo not speak at all with the patient or their family.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.48,0:29:50.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, just one time more\NI need to speak with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.80,0:29:53.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hear the story of the patients in one talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.96,0:29:56.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.80,0:30:01.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.04,0:30:04.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's a big mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.68,0:30:08.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The virtuoso of psychotherapy\N is not getting sympathetic to the patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.44,0:30:15.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, the ones that have been monitoring were you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.04,0:30:18.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\3c&H585657&}Sorry about doing something on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.12,0:30:21.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, I was worried about Yumiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.04,0:30:23.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.96,0:30:26.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So then, what do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.96,0:30:31.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,From the husband's room, very early in the morning,\Nthere were a loud voice and a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.08,0:30:33.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Voice and sound?\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.20,0:30:38.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, later this morning, without any other incident,\N he just went to work in 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.56,0:30:42.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A loud voice and a sound..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.20,0:30:49.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.65,0:31:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, even though it's a bit of poor sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.65,0:31:07.64,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Chronic lack of sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.64,0:31:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.14,0:31:11.66,Self tought,,0,0,0,,irritating moodiness
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.66,0:31:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If one of us is full of stress,\Nis more likely to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.71,0:31:17.21,Self tought,,0,0,0,,carrying stress everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.65,0:31:20.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.65,0:31:24.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to try
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.64,0:31:42.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.14,0:31:45.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.14,0:31:51.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.15,0:31:54.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.63,0:31:58.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,ah.. since also today, I'm going to stay here,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.69,0:32:01.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you need something..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.64,0:32:04.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good night.\NYeah, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.13,0:32:10.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.15,0:32:14.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.15,0:32:16.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.71,0:32:20.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.74,0:32:22.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.16,0:32:25.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.15,0:32:28.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.08,0:32:33.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry for the intrusion,\Nbut you see, I had a sleepless night,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.44,0:32:35.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I know it's shameless, but I ask you this favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.80,0:32:38.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,since there isn't any other duty room empty,\Nexcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.92,0:32:40.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll ask your help in sharing the room only tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.00,0:32:42.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.15,0:32:46.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.62,0:32:51.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.64,0:32:58.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder what is Dr. Hino thinking to do..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.20,0:33:27.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't think he can do this\Nfor many nights, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.12,0:33:46.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hi, excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.16,0:33:49.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,yes.. I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.73,0:33:54.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,yes.. I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.14,0:33:57.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.66,0:33:59.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.62,0:34:02.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.63,0:34:05.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm not sorry!! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.63,0:34:07.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.63,0:34:09.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.72,0:34:15.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey!\N{\3c&H585657&}Kobayashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.14,0:34:17.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.13,0:34:21.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.15,0:34:22.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.13,0:34:24.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It hurts, hurts, hurts\Nhurts, hurts, hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.65,0:34:26.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,hurts, hurts, hurts!\N{\3c&H585657&}Dr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.18,0:34:55.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.68,0:34:57.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.18,0:35:02.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That wound? how?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.25,0:35:04.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've heard that recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.67,0:35:08.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you can't sleep well,\Nyou have lack of sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.16,0:35:09.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.66,0:35:13.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Have you experienced something different\Nwhile sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.68,0:35:15.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.65,0:35:18.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When having a relatively light REM sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.69,0:35:22.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the things that happen in the dream,\Nwould in fact trigger real actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.77,0:35:27.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For example, if while dreaming you're shouting,\Nyou would be really shouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.66,0:35:32.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If in the dream you're hitting,\Nyou would be really hitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.15,0:35:37.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Such condition is called\NREM sleep behavior disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.17,0:35:52.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So it was me after all..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.67,0:35:55.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why she couldn't look me in the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.52,0:36:03.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.\NTo do such a thing even to the Dr..
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.00,0:36:04.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.25,0:36:11.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For a long time, vaguely,\NI've been having this strange feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.67,0:36:13.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.18,0:36:18.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, if I think about it,\NI wasn't conscious of this doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.18,0:36:20.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.67,0:36:25.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, whys is it\Nthat my wife didn't tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.17,0:36:27.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If I was the one causing the injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.72,0:36:32.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If it was me and my head what was acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.68,0:36:37.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't see why\Nmy wife is not hating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.68,0:36:41.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If I consider it myself,\NI no longer understand myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.67,0:36:49.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, she is like,\Nthis time, even the previous time, just said
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.76,0:36:54.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"I'm fine,\Nit was only that I feel down the stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.67,0:36:59.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,don't worry, just go to work" she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.15,0:37:01.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's all, she didn't say anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.69,0:37:03.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.68,0:37:07.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Maybe your wife was also puzzled,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.18,0:37:10.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and thinking about her usual kind husband,\Ndidn't want to say
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.20,0:37:13.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to you the truth about this matter.\N Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.19,0:37:19.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,yeah, that might be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.18,0:37:24.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you have seen my wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.68,0:37:28.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that was all,\Nwe no longer speak about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.17,0:37:31.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,while I was doing such a horrible thing..
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.18,0:37:41.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,while I was doing such a horrible thing..
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.16,0:37:46.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So scared she couldn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.17,0:37:51.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm a pathetic men.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.73,0:37:56.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're not pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.66,0:37:59.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can see it very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.17,0:38:04.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi-san has a strong sense of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.67,0:38:09.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So I think that in order to seek for a perfect resolution,\Nyou would do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.66,0:38:12.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your own weaknesses and also
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.21,0:38:14.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,your own mistakes,\Nyou won't just accept them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.76,0:38:16.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And because you love your wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.68,0:38:19.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and because you don't want to disappoint your wife
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.67,0:38:23.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Aiming for extra perfection,\NI'm sure you are working really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.67,0:38:26.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can see that very clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.66,0:38:33.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Accepting yourself is a very difficult thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.75,0:38:37.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because there aren't just good things,\Nthere are also a lot of defects
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.67,0:38:43.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But she has accept you,\Nall of you with the good and the bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.68,0:38:46.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think it's a great thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.20,0:38:54.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.77,0:39:00.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.17,0:39:04.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,First,\Nlet's consider your disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.66,0:39:07.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NLet's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.65,0:39:14.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.69,0:39:19.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is a disease that is said to develop if there is a problem\N with the function of the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.68,0:39:22.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If it's treat it it can improve in most cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.16,0:39:24.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's a disease that develops well.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.65,0:39:28.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In this case,\Nby adding extreme stress,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.17,0:39:32.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it seems that it made the symptoms\Nnot easy to appear
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.68,0:39:37.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Stress?\N{\3c&H585657&}Any sort of big anxiety
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.25,0:39:40.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You don't have to burden it by yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.68,0:39:54.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,for your wife's sake too
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.68,0:39:57.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,First,\Nwhy don't we start with an examination?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.17,0:40:08.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.16,0:40:12.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.18,0:40:26.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.67,0:41:27.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"You're not alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.19,0:41:29.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"Let's drink tea together."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.68,0:41:34.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The legislator of the government political party,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.18,0:41:37.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}has received the illegal donation of 20 million yen \Nfrom the security company,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.17,0:41:39.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of the Tokyo Metropolitan Police Department OB chaired officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.18,0:41:42.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Today's daily special looks good, right?\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.24,0:41:44.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, let's eat.\N{\3c&H585657&}Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.67,0:41:48.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Furthermore, the incumbent of the Metropolitan Police Dept. incumbent,\Nis also going to be prosecuted for this issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.16,0:41:50.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Also the Superintendent Kobayashi Tsukasa..{\i0}\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.68,0:41:53.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The facts of this illegal donations had been concealed for a long time..
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.68,0:41:55.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.70,0:41:59.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi-san, please calm down!\NLet 
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.74,0:42:01.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,please, calm down!\N{\3c&H585657&}Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.66,0:42:05.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Where did that psychiatrist go!?\NLet me go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.16,0:42:09.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Minister,\Nthis is another fraud from the government allied party, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.15,0:42:11.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ugh ... no ....
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.17,0:42:13.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so.. that ....
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.17,0:42:16.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,those are space aliens..
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.66,0:42:26.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I would like to closely explained the circumstances, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.16,0:42:30.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of the incident of the previous question{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.15,0:42:32.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1} today, and openly ....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.17,0:42:35.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Today's Ike-san is stirring.. 
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.19,0:42:38.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you also want to ask soba?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.76,0:42:40.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.00,0:42:46.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumiko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.66,0:43:01.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, you're an awful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.67,0:43:08.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What I was trying to protect,\Nyou crushed it all..
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.17,0:43:12.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, now that the politician fraud has been accused,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.66,0:43:14.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.68,0:43:17.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It wasn't just my husband,\Nhe wasn't the only one being used!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.68,0:43:22.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And though he did anything wrong..\NYet, this thing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.17,0:43:28.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's all the doctor's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.18,0:43:29.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.68,0:43:34.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To that person,\NI wasn't able to give him a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.67,0:43:37.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and he cherishes me without blaming me even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.65,0:43:42.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even though he was really busy,\Nhe found a Gerbera and bought it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.68,0:43:47.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Being just the two of us at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.68,0:43:52.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,he always protects me as a treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.67,0:43:57.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So this time,\Nit was my turn to protect him!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.22,0:44:03.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., you have the tendency to misunderstand everything..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.66,0:44:07.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why did you break us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.68,0:44:21.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,These were 'preserved flowers', right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.21,0:44:26.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Its moment of beauty is confined\Nby immersing them in a special fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.17,0:44:29.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,eh.. what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.69,0:44:35.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumiko-san, what you were trying to protect\Nthe thing you didn't want to be destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.68,0:44:39.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,isn't something similar to the 'preserved flowers'?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.20,0:44:46.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Aren't you trying to lock up the shape of happiness inside of yourself\Nconfining it inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.65,0:44:48.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,confine?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.67,0:44:52.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was glad to remain in that way!\NOnly if I could put up with it..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.18,0:44:58.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was..\NI was okay anyhow!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.18,0:45:01.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It isn't the case to be okay anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.69,0:45:06.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumiko-san you're not fine anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.16,0:45:12.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your husband,\Nas you mentioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.16,0:45:15.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is a respectable person with a strong sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.17,0:45:18.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why this time,\Nfor the sake of heading towards to your happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.67,0:45:21.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think he took a new step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.67,0:45:26.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a wonderful thing? Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.69,0:45:39.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your husband has placed here,\Na white Gerbera.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.67,0:45:42.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you familiar with the flower language?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.18,0:46:00.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.17,0:46:08.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It means 'hope'
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.15,0:46:11.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.19,0:46:18.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You are the hope for your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.16,0:46:23.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You are an important person for your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.67,0:46:28.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're not fine anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.16,0:46:32.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.18,0:46:36.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumiko-san, for your husband's sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.26,0:46:40.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,for your own sake too,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.67,0:46:43.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,please, how about searching for happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.67,0:46:51.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.16,0:46:54.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If there's something that troubles you,\NI'll be willing to listen to you at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.68,0:46:57.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm your and your husband's ally
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.23,0:47:02.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The door of my examination room is always open.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.17,0:47:09.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.16,0:47:12.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be leaving for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.60,0:47:15.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.17,0:47:42.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.18,0:47:59.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here, please.\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.28,0:48:13.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.67,0:48:22.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.17,0:48:28.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About the issue of Kobayashi Yumiko-san changing hospital\Nshe has withdrawn the request.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.16,0:48:36.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Was Hino-kun the one that uncovered\N the illegal donations of politicians?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.27,0:48:38.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just like a detective, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.67,0:48:41.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's an interesting candidate for professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.16,0:48:44.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.18,0:48:50.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think he will return immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.18,0:48:52.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please take a seat and wait here.\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.24,0:48:59.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.67,0:49:35.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.16,0:49:39.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since Yumeno-san came,\NI've asked her to wait in the examination room.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.18,0:49:43.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.17,0:49:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.68,0:49:57.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san, sorry to keep you waiting..
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.65,0:50:08.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello,\NI see you were able to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.21,0:50:13.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,why..
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.17,0:50:21.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Always by yourself..
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.17,0:50:25.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,always you're so lonely, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.68,0:50:33.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay now, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.25,0:50:36.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.16,0:50:40.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because..
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.67,0:50:43.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.16,0:50:50.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A doctor of the heart.
